DO NOT attempt to automatically fix:
- Multiple migration heads
- Migration conflicts
- Dependency issues

ALWAYS ask user to run diagnostics first:
- alembic heads
- alembic current  
- alembic history

ONLY generate migration code when user provides:
- Specific revision IDs
- Clear strategy (merge/reset)
- Model changes to implement